snippet.title: Johnny Depp Vs. Amber Heard: The Complete Story
snippet.description:
This case has been a continuous bombshell! Most people still do not know the entire story however. So I wanted to make a video giving the entire story as best as I could without making the video super long. This case is incredibly long anyways and has many many points, but to give everyone the full story and the genuine idea of everything going on, I did my very best to include all the important high points without making the video too extremely long. 

I want to give special thanks to a few channels, without their hard work and research this video would have taken me much longer.
So special thanks to:
 ThatUmbrellaGuy,
Popcorn Planet, 
Incredibly Average

These three channels have amazing videos on this subject!

Links to audio: 
https://youtu.be/Cg9SvQSMnoE - Incredibly Average - audio of Amber telling Johnny no one will believe him.

https://youtu.be/aca0KWoHtqQ - Incredibly Average - The real abuser finally revealed (audio. 1 hour long)

https://youtu.be/XiuUzvZMyro - Amber Fighting with Johnny

https://youtu.be/Lc4hf4w7QXA - Amber Mocking Johnny Depp (come save me)

https://youtu.be/k9pbrBmHI58 - Full audio tape (uncut audio)

This video was  made and produced by Cyberlink Powerdirector 365 19
The audio used in this video was produced by Cyberlink Audio Director

I want to thank everyone who spoke to me about this case and all the lawyers and law students who helped me understand all of the legal jargon.

The Makeup Used in This Video: 
Illamasqua Hydra Veil
Yenza - Tone Up Primer
Anastasia Beaverly Hills Luminous Foundation in shade 120W
NO. 7 - Lift and Luminate Serum Concealer in shade - "Fair"
NYX Born To Glow Radiant Concealer in shade "Pale"
Tarte Shape Tape Setting Powder in shade "Translucent"
NYX Cream Contour Palette in shade "Light/Clair"
TreStique Mini Brow Pencil
Morphe @James Charles Palette for the "Black" eyeshadow
@NikkieTutorials + @BEAUTY BAY Eye Shadow Palette shade in "IVY"
NYX Glitter Primer 
NYX Glitter Brillants in shade "GLI 10"
NYX Epic Ink Liner
Lash Princess false lash effect waterproof mascara 
Aesthetica - Sunset Bronzer contour 
Tarte Maracuja Miracle Mist - setting spray
OFRA Highlighter Covent Garden
Eye Lashes - Ardell
Eye Lash Glue - Kiss clear glue.


IF you would like to follow me on social media!! I would really appreciate it! Here are my links

Facebook - Metal Momma

Twitter - @Ananiachanda

Instagram - Metalmomma5114

TikTok - metalmomma0
